Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller

Class InMatchCallback

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.InMatchCallback
All Implemented Interfaces:
Consumer<com.google.gson.JsonObject>
public class InMatchCallback extends Object implements Consumer<com.google.gson.JsonObject>
This class represents a BiConsumer<JsonObject, Dispatcher> to be set to a Dispatcher (through Dispatcher.setOnReceive(Consumer)) when the Dispatcher is connected to a Match. It makes the Dispatcher return an error message if the player tries to send another CREATE or JOIN message.
